citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:40 AM on
06JUN2023.
Inspector attempted to contact licensee by calling both cell phone numbers associated with the account. The licensee
returned the phone call and stated there was no one available to conduct an animal welfare inspection today.
The facility was not able to be inspected for compliance with the Animal Welfare Act, regulations and standards to ensure
the health and well-being of the animals.
Additional Inspectors:
JUSTINE O MALLEY, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
